    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "come on, i'm not trying to be dramatic. i literally just had a massive amount of pepperoni and cheese. my whole stomach is bloated too. it's definitely just gas or reflux. if i take a high dose of antacids like maybe 4 or 5 at once, won't that just neutralize the acid and make the chest thing go away? i'd rather just fix it here than spend 5 hours in an er waiting room for nothing.",
